"We lift the weight
of the entire world!"

1934
02:48:47,661 --> 02:48:51,658
"People arrive and depart,"

1935
02:48:51,875 --> 02:48:56,471
"but we remain here."

1936
02:48:56,561 --> 02:49:01,157
"We lift the weight
of the entire world!"

1937
02:49:01,247 --> 02:49:06,145
"We lift the weight
of the entire world!"

1938
02:49:06,235 --> 02:49:10,522
"We lift it."

1939
